      "id": "PopularPost57928",
      "post_content": "Fun with [Krark's Thumb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb) ([Mirror Gallery](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror Gallery) optional). Maybe throw in [Urza's Armor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Urza's Armor) or [Sphere of Law](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sphere of Law) (or perhaps even [Glacial Chasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glacial Chasm) or a concurrent [Samite Ministration](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Samite Ministration)) for insurance. I mean, hey, there's only a 12.5% chance (three heads) that the clash will be forced to end, and if you're not taking any damage...",
