    {
      "id": "PopularPost93305",
      "post_content": "I did a bit of simulation to evaluate this card. Here's what I came up with, using 10 million iterations with a pseudo-random coin flip.   \n  \nWith no [Krark's Thumb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb)s in play:  \nAverage 1.92 damage to you  \nAverage 1.96 damage to your opponent  \n  \nWith one [Krark's Thumb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb) in play (assuming you always choose to keep the flip going, even if this will kill you. Dumb I know, but it gets the point across number-wise):  \n3.97 damage to you  \n3.98 damage to your opponent  \n  \nWith two [Krark's Thumb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb)s and a [Mirror Gallery](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror Gallery) in play (same algorithm as with one thumb. Note that with two Thumbs in play, you flip 4 coins each run instead of 1):  \n16.00 damage to you  \n16.00 damage to your opponent  \n  \nWith three [Krark's Thumb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb)s and a [Mirror Gallery](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror Gallery) in play (8 flips):  \n255.98 damage to you  \n255.91 damage to your opponent  \n  \nNotice a pattern? 2^1, 2^2, 2^4, 2^8. I predict with four Thumbs, the damage would avera... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Guest513736147",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost93305\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I did a bit of simulation to evaluate this card. Here's what I came up with, using 10 million iterations with a pseudo-random coin flip. <br/><br/>With no <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krark's Thumb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb\">Krark's Thumb</a>s in play:<br/>Average 1.92 damage to you<br/>Average 1.96 damage to your opponent<br/><br/>With one <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krark's Thumb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb\">Krark's Thumb</a> in play (assuming you always choose to keep the flip going, even if this will kill you. Dumb I know, but it gets the point across number-wise):<br/>3.97 damage to you<br/>3.98 damage to your opponent<br/><br/>With two <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krark's Thumb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb\">Krark's Thumb</a>s and a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mirror Gallery\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror Gallery\">Mirror Gallery</a> in play (same algorithm as with one thumb. Note that with two Thumbs in play, you flip 4 coins each run instead of 1):<br/>16.00 damage to you<br/>16.00 damage to your opponent<br/><br/>With three <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krark's Thumb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb\">Krark's Thumb</a>s and a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mirror Gallery\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror Gallery\">Mirror Gallery</a> in play (8 flips):<br/>255.98 damage to you<br/>255.91 damage to your opponent<br/><br/>Notice a pattern? 2^1, 2^2, 2^4, 2^8. I predict with four Thumbs, the damage would avera... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 93305)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '93305'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42309\">Guest513736147</span>\r\n                                (8/5/2010 12:32:46 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class